{
  "stem": "3928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, that's when this friend of mine told me this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why don't I go in, because his brother was one of the, what they call a camp-- pre-- what they called, an assemble camp, for the concentration camp, and try to get him out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I made-- in the headquarters, I made up a paper, which says this, you know, for myself, to cover myself, this I, George Nemeth, in-- the liaison officer for the German headquarters, and I ordered-- I-- by order of the headquarters, everybody should cooperate with me and follow my orders.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wiedemayer signed it again, naturally, which was me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And with this paper, I went into the-- this assembly camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told them, I'm looking for a person who has an information what we urgently needed, military information.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they lined up a couple thousand people for me, in a row, so I can drive through with my car.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a-- a-- a Hungarian-- a German officer was with me, in the car, you know, from the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they told me, let me know if you see the person, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So finally, I find him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I pointed out, that's the one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I stopped the car.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He jumped out the car, and he took him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- he told him that you sit in the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At this point, he was with him, another guy, who was my schoolmate, also, like him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as he yelled out, he come out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, take me, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Take me, too, with you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fortunately, the German officer didn't know what he was saying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I just went there, and I punched him out, you know, because this was the difference.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
